The paper presents a new algorithm for hierarchical clustering with general linkage functions, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. The paper also discusses the scalability of the algorithm and compares it with other scalable methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
